This paper proposes a novel 3D enhancement convolutional neural network (3DECNN) to improve the spatial resolution of CT studies. The paper focuses on image enhancement using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) techniques. Finally, the paper uses neural networks (cs.NE) to achieve its objectives.
